sections.heading: Violations; proceedings; subornation of perjury
sections.text: Whoever shall knowingly prepare, or cause to be prepared, a report, return, or answer required by sections 59-801 to 59-831 that is false, as aforesaid, shall be guilty of subornation of perjury and punished by law.SourceLaws 1905, c. 162, ยง 21, p. 645
